How to manage the Event Types?

On creating or editing an Event you'll probably notice the Event Type field.

It's the method for your company to separate the events into categories - be it
by the service type that your providing or by the event's format.

To manage the Event Types, go to mobilize events Homepage.

At your right, click on the (...) button and then on "Manage Event Types", just like
shown in the image below.
[img]
